# TwinMind does not require server-side environment variables to run.
#
# The Groq API key is entered at runtime by the user on the in-app Settings
# page. It lives in the browser's sessionStorage for the tab lifetime only
# and is forwarded per-request as the `x-groq-key` header. Server routes
# proxy straight to api.groq.com and never persist, log, or cache the key.
#
# Optional overrides (all have sensible defaults — leave unset in most cases):
#
# NEXT_TELEMETRY_DISABLED=1
